sentence: The S&P 500 was little changed on Tuesday following a three-day rally as a drop in Apple shares overshadowed optimism from remarks made by U.S. and China officials in pledging firm commitment to a Phase One trade deal.
ET, the Dow Jones Industrial Average .DJI was down 0.53% at 28,157.7.
The S&P 500 .SPX was down 0.01% at 3,430.91 and the Nasdaq Composite .IXIC was up 0.15% at 11,397.203.
